testcase.title: 001)Check Chinese locale is displayed on PressRelease for localization

steps.title: I logged in as a "Localization" user with access to "CE-4" project
the "HomePage" page should be loaded on log on with Locale Dropdown
I verify "Chinese" language should listed under the Locale Dropdown and Select check-box against Chinese
I perform Quick Search by term "cancer"
I click on press release dataset in the result page
I click on "random" report link from the results table
I click on press release snapshot
I Verify Ch translation for "PressRelease" page
I Verify the localization on "PressRelease" report
